<collectingCountry id="A9FBDFFAFFAEFF9BFC76FD476313D5A9" box="[981,1077,706,729]" name="Morocco" pageId="4" pageNumber="4">Morocco</collectingCountry>
but differs from it in larger autozooecial apertures (average aperture width 
<quantity id="1614328FFFAEFF9BFA9EFD6462BAD589" box="[1341,1436,737,761]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.2" pageId="4" pageNumber="4" unit="mm" value="0.22">0.22 mm</quantity>
